    <div class="card-logo">
      <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dcfmvazgl/image/upload/v1736335480/Wash%20portfolio/paszkowicz_f2hmp5.png" alt="Paszkowicz-Group">
    </div>
    <div class="card-text">

      <div class="card-title">
        <h1>Front-End Web Developers</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="card-parapgraph">
        <p>As front-end web developers with advanced
          training from Le Wagon in Lille, France, we
          specialize in crafting visually appealing
          and highly interactive user interfaces. We
          prioritize responsiveness and smooth user
          experiences across all devices. With expertise
